SHADOWRUN Spell-Generator

1.0 DESCRIPTION OF THE PROGRAM

                              SpellGenerator

the program should works on all computersystems like Amiga, PC, Linux, ...
it is shell-oriented, it means, all datainputs are done in the shell.
the output can be chosen by TeX or ASCII. its done by the option -t,
-p will create a spelldesignform like this one in the end of the
grimoire. it containts the factors, which influences the drain.
the fileformat hat .txt. the TeX or ASCII-file includes a full description
with .tex or .doc.

options :
 -l   language       possible:   e und g
                     standard:   g
 -p   spellform      possible:   PAPER/Paper/paper
                     standard:   no spellform
 -s   filename       Standard:   zauber
 -t   outputformat   possible:   TeX/TEX/Tex/tex or ASCII/Ascii/ascii
                     standard:   TeX

Version : AMIGA        zauber 1.01
          LINUX        zauber 1.01
          HPUNIX       zauber 1.00

